Esme Hubbard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esme_Hubbard 0 Esme Hubbard (1880-12 April 1951) was a British actress of the silent era.She was born Esme Woodbine Hubbard to British parents in Russia and died in Ealing, London in 1951 at age 71.
